data.description: Come and check out this clean and tidy 3 bed, 2 bath ranch home with a country setting and small town amenities like ciity sewer, water, and fiber internet! Completely updated home with new stainless steel appliances! The wood burning fireplace keeps the whole house warm and there's an outdoor brick smoker!  3 city lots mean room to build or play and lots of privacy on the edge of town. Raise some chickens and your kids in the idyllic small-town setting just 20 minutes from St. Joseph and less than an hour from KC!
